.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, watermelon, peas, banana
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, board-games, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: frog, horse, cat, mouse
1. the person eating watermelon is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
6. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
7. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | peas   | banana      | watermelon       | asparagus |
| Hobby   | hiking | puzzles | board-games     | reading |
| Pet     | mouse     | horse  | frog | cat |

