.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, iced-tea, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, family, zombie
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, snake, mouse
1. the owner of the snake is the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the person watching zombie movies and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking cola##1
8. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | juice          | sprite | cola        |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | fantasy | zombie   | superhero     |
| Pet           | rabbit | goldfish         | mouse         | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, cooking, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, police-officer, manager, teacher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, soul, funk
1. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
2. the manager is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the teacher is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the project-manager and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
6. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the manager##3
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | card-games | hiking      | cooking       | magic-tricks    |
| Job           | police-officer  | manager  | teacher | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | soul | gospel         | hip-hop    |

