.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, analyst, paramedic, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, hot-chocolate-polo, cricket
1. the architect is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the architect##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the architect##3
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo##3
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the architect##1
7. the architect is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the analyst is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the fisherman is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | sprite         | lemonade  | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate         |
| Job        | fisherman | analyst | architect | paramedic         |
| Sport      | snowboarding         | hot-chocolate-polo  | cycling   | cricket |

