.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, rock, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, mexican, australian, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: goat, frog, snake, guinea-pig
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 2. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the australian is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##2
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan of rock##1
 7. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
 9. the mexican is between the fan of ambient and the fan of rock##2
10. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | rock    | dubstep | ambient    |
| Nationality   | colombian | australian | mexican  | pakistani |
| Pet           | snake   | guinea-pig    | goat        | frog   |

