.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, water, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, project-manager, firefighter, bartender
There are 4 different nationalities: german, turkish, brazilian, egyptian
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
2. the project-manager is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
4. the project-manager is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the electrician##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the project-manager##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the project-manager##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the turkish##3
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate                | cola  | mirinda | water   |
| Job           | bartender | project-manager | electrician   | firefighter |
| Nationality   | turkish         | german     | egyptian     | brazilian |

