.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, zucchini, onion, asparagus
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel, comedy, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, techno, soul, disco
1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
4. the person eating onion is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the fan of house is between the person watching crime movies and the fan of disco##2
6. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | onion    | zucchini  | asparagus  | blueberry |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | time-travel | fantasy | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | house     | disco    | techno |

