.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, water, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, russian, indian, canadian
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rabbit, chinchilla
1. the owner of the ferret is between the person drinking water and the spanish##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
3. the indian is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the russian##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
7. the spanish is on the left or right of the canadian##3
8. the indian is the person drinking juice##1
9. the canadian is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | juice | water      | 7up  | soy-milk    |
| Nationality   | indian   | russian | canadian | spanish |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | rabbit       | ferret   | bird      |

