.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, nigerian, canadian, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, soccer, cricket, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is climbing##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the american is between the person who's sport is climbing and the polish##2
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
8. the nigerian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | traveling | rock-climbing  | woodworking  |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian       | american | polish |
| Sport         | cricket   | climbing      | swimming | soccer       |

