.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, milk, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, western, thriller
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the pony is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person drinking milk is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
6. the person watching animation movies is the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the owner of the rat is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | milk      | iced-tea | fanta     | coffee    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | animation      | musical | western |
| Pet           | rabbit   | pony  | turtle     | rat |

