.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, golf, climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, ship, taxi
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking coffee is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is golf##2
6. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | coffee     | soy-milk    | juice        |
| Sport       | golf   | weightlifting | snowboarding | climbing |
| Transport   | taxi | ship      | jet-ski    | boat   |

