The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, scientific, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, american, canadian, indonesian
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is between the american and the person eating lettuce##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
4. the person eating kiwi is on the far left or far right##3
5. the japanese is on the left of the american##1
6. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
7. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating lettuce is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | kiwi | lettuce  | spinach   | pumpkin    |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | scientific     | time-travel | satire |
| Nationality   | canadian   | indonesian | japanese | american   |

