The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, pop, salsa, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indian, argentine, pakistani
1. the pakistani is in an even position##4
2. the american is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person watching animation movies is the american##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the argentine##1
7. the argentine is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
8. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | disaster | animation | action   |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | hip-hop   | salsa     | metal    |
| Nationality   | indian  | argentine | american  | pakistani |

