.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, pumpkin, garlic, corn
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, video-games, collecting, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, cat, ferret
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
4. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | garlic    | pumpkin    | kiwi  | corn |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | video-games | singing | collecting      |
| Pet     | goldfish   | snake        | ferret   | cat       |

 